snippet: Militants stormed an African Union base after an explosive-laden car rammed into the gates, and scores of soldiers and militants were killed in the gun battle that followed.

byline.contributor: Hussein Mohamed contributed reporting from Mogadishu, Somalia.

lead_paragraph: Militants stormed an African Union base after an explosive-laden car rammed into the gates, and scores of soldiers and militants were killed in the gun battle that followed.

headline.main: Shabab Attack in Somalia Sets Off Predawn Gun Battle
